author: scottbw
msg: Fix for WOOKIE-94 (part of WOOKIE-67) implementing folder-based localization using a servlet filter. Includes test cases. Note that this does slow down a Wookie server as all static resource requests get intercepted, so we should also look into caching or other performance optimisation methods for this solution.
